data.description: Surprisingly spacious gem situated in the perfect location close to exciting new developments and restaurants. This home is part of a well maintained, quiet, and friendly neighborhood, ensuring a peaceful atmosphere for you to enjoy. New interior paint! Features open concept living, three spacious bedrooms, vaulted ceilings, bamboo floors, ample natural light, fenced back yard space, attached garage, Hazeldale Elementary across the way. Primary bedroom comes complete with an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. It has everything you need and just waiting for your personal touch.
